data.description: A wonderful A frame home sitting on 1 acre, surrounded by wrought iron fence, this 5 bed, 3 1/2 bath, 3 story home is a treasure. This custom kitchen has too many built - ins and features to list. From custom hidden pop outs for your mixer to clever hide always for your utensils. Every pot, pan and dish has a home. The backsplash above the triple sink is 100 year old Japanese fishing boat wood. Custom floors dominate the the landscape of the massive open floor plan, continuing to the custom stairs onto the second floor landing. Walk out of the master bedroom into a tiled, window filled sunroom. The second floor features two more bedrooms and another full bathroom. The third floor has another two bedrooms and another fully remodeled bathroom. Every room has an exit to a deck. New roof put on in 2020. New downstairs A/C system installed in 2021. City water and well water. Separate garage with two additional storage units and an additional carport. New refrigerator. New dishwasher.
